@HostAddress = http://localhost:5080

### Submit a support email

POST {{HostAddress}}/api/support/emails
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Sender": "developer@example.com",
  "Subject": "Bug in Application A order processing",
  "Body": "The OrderController is returning a 500 error when processing orders with null shipping addresses. This is affecting production users in Application A."
}

### Get workflow state by issue ID

GET {{HostAddress}}/api/support/issues/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### List all processed issues

GET {{HostAddress}}/api/support/issues

### Stream workflow updates (SSE)

GET {{HostAddress}}/api/support/stream

### Get current state of all AI agents

GET {{HostAddress}}/api/support/agents
